{"tid":217696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教官涉騙學警9萬元","createTime":"2017-04-26T03:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T11:27:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"084f0a5055735abf3b0303b8c881b7cdeb7c1c57","tid":217696,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20002218&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20002218%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170426&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=58a9b12a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20002218%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170426&h=7952df4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20002218&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170426</a><br />\n<br />\n教官涉騙學警9萬元<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警隊再爆醜聞。47歲警校男教官涉嫌以權謀私，詐騙學員雜費，涉及9萬多港元，警方早前接獲投訴，交由港島總區重案組接手調查，昨將涉案男教官拘捕帶署。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n警隊再爆出醜聞，有男教官涉騙學警逾9萬元。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n疑收日常雜費做手腳<br />\n<br />\n被捕男教官暫准保釋候查，下月中旬向警方報到。案情指該教官涉於2012至2013年在警察學院擔任學警訓練副班主任期間，詐騙學員雜費，涉9萬多港元。據了解，有學員不滿其行為，懷疑有人濫權自肥，向警方投訴，警方高層甚為重視，由港島總區重案組接手調查。探員經調查後昨採取行動，以涉嫌詐騙將該教官逮捕。<br />\n警方發言人表示，警隊非常重視人員操守，任何人員違法，警隊定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n據悉，學警在警察學院受訓，一般包住不包食，伙食及洗衫等雜費須自付。消息人士指，教官能出蠱惑的地方，可能涉及大夥人夾錢的項目，例如為支付日常雜費開支，每名學警每月夾兩、三百元，多數交由教官保管，學員一般絕少要求核數，若有人存心詐騙，該筆錢易被人做手腳。<br />\n■記者曾海帆"},{"pid":"591bf7e17164ebb0d5a8859a2829f52080d4efe1","tid":217696,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"呀sir呃錢唔駛你教"},{"pid":"6061d5069955d3d0b854ebb55952bf81ab33b7da","tid":217696,"uid":31787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"我諗教官食水唔係第一日既事<br />\n<br />\n每月一個人起碼比四位數<br />\n之後自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273f0f9b26e8a35bc0ba234a7150d706d0224d83","tid":217696,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7587d35d457a6799431bdcbf2857c3d965583da","tid":217696,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"呢個係警校傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150d83f6a7d93d719f49f017371eb39d75da8262","tid":217696,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"8ee08639d7bb29878a1c171907aaf5bc73b07e58","tid":217696,"uid":582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"警察貪污好正常姐"},{"pid":"dbfad7a65a194c3d86cd32609513ef270a0774ec","tid":217696,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"身教 比 言教 重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d883afa3503d0cc6c6a3ec70d48ec52b2157aa","tid":217696,"uid":59358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"休班警 , 當值警 , 退休警 .......今次係教官警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74691157f6d6f94a8715971cba22ab1ff6df19a2","tid":217696,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"阿蛇收黑唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdf13432ba6abbdd16a21f0c8ab81451715e116","tid":217696,"uid":11667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"阿sir收片唔使你教"},{"pid":"8d77fe05a09027c676773be26a9e43b22ad56f59","tid":217696,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"呢班新仔無運行喇<br />\n打破人地傳統"},{"p